---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="How it works — nag."
  description="The four-step nag loop: add, set cadence, do it, see the dots. Plus cadence types, skip vs miss, and FAQs."
  current="how-it-works"
>
  <!-- ──────── Page header ──────── -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="padding-top: 80px;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="kicker">How it works</div>
      <h1 class="h-display" style="margin-top: 18px;">
        add. set cadence.<br />
        do it. see the dots<span class="dot">.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lede" style="margin-top: 28px;">
        Four moves. No onboarding wizard, no setup quiz, no "let's get to know
        you." You know yourself fine.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ──────── Four steps ──────── -->
  <section style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <div class="step-fig step-tile-wrap">
            <div class="step-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5v17H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5z"></path>
                    <path d="M20 5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-5v17h5a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad">daily</div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">read 20 min</div>
              <div class="t-last">2h ago</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell missed"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell today-done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Add the habit</h3>
          <p>Plain text. A verb and a thing. Skip the categories.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <div class="step-fig step-tile-wrap">
            <div class="step-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <path d="M6 6v12M18 6v12M3 9v6M21 9v6M6 12h12"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad">m·w·f</div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">gym</div>
              <div class="t-last">yesterday</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Set the cadence</h3>
          <p>How often, which days, how many times. Nag does the math.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <div class="step-fig step-notif">
            <div class="notif-card">
              <span class="brand-mark notif-app-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <span class="row">
                  <span class="d"></span>
                  <span class="d"></span>
                  <span class="d"></span>
                  <span class="d miss"></span>
                  <span class="d"></span>
                  <span class="d"></span>
                  <span class="d today"></span>
                </span>
                <span class="wm">nag</span>
              </span>
              <div class="notif-body">
                <div class="notif-head">
                  <span class="notif-title">nag · 2 due now</span>
                  <span class="notif-time">9:00 AM</span>
                </div>
                <div class="notif-msg">
                  still waiting<span class="dot">.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="notif-sub">vitamins · read 20 min</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Get nagged</h3>
          <p>
            Scheduled habits trigger a notification at their time. Multiple
            habits in the same slot? One consolidated nag. Already checked in or
            skipped? Silence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">04</div>
          <div class="step-fig">
            <div
              style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--nag-mute);"
            >
              last 4 weeks
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 3px;"
              >
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: rgba(26,20,16,0.08); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: rgba(26,20,16,0.08); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: rgba(26,20,16,0.08); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: var(--nag-ink); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; border: 1.5px solid var(--nag-orange); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="cell"
                  style="aspect-ratio: 1; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 3px;"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--nag-mute); margin-top: 8px;"
              >
                compliance · 86%
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>See the truth</h3>
          <p>Dots show what you actually did. Not what you meant to.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ──────── Long-press shortcut ──────── -->
  <section
    style="padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 96px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 96px);"
  >
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="longpress">
        <div class="longpress-body">
          <span class="kicker" style="color: var(--nag-orange);">Fast path</span
          >
          <h2
            class="h-1"
            style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4.6vw, 56px); margin-top: 8px;"
          >
            Long-press to check in<span class="dot">.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="lede" style="max-width: 50ch;">
            Don't open the habit. Don't tap through.
            <strong>Press and hold any tile</strong>
            to log a check-in right there on the home board. Haptic tick, dot flips,
            you're done. Two seconds, total.
          </p>
          <ul class="longpress-list">
            <li>
              <span class="lp-bullet"></span>Long-press for an instant check-in
            </li>
            <li><span class="lp-bullet"></span>Long-press again to undo it</li>
            <li>
              <span class="lp-bullet"></span>Tap once to drill in &amp; see
              detail / skip
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="longpress-fig">
          <div class="longpress-stage">
            <div class="longpress-ripple"></div>
            <div class="mock-tile longpress-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5v17H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5z"></path>
                    <path d="M20 5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-5v17h5a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad">daily</div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">read 20 min</div>
              <div class="t-last">checking in…</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell today-done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="longpress-finger" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="longpress-caption">
            <span
              class="mono"
              style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--nag-mute); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;"
              >hold</span
            >
            <span
              class="mono"
              style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--nag-orange); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;"
              >→ checked in</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ──────── Anatomy ──────── -->
  <section style="background: var(--nag-cream-2);">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="kicker">Anatomy</span>
        <h2 class="h-1">A tile, decoded<span class="dot">.</span></h2>
        <p class="lede">
          Every habit on the home board is a tile. The structure is always the
          same — icon, cadence, name, last check-in, week strip — but what's in
          each slot changes with the habit. Five examples:
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tile-examples">
        <!-- 01 · Daily, simple text cadence -->
        <div class="tile-example">
          <div class="tile-example-stage">
            <div class="mock-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5v17H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5z"></path>
                    <path d="M20 5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-5v17h5a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad">daily</div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">read 20 min</div>
              <div class="t-last">2h ago</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell today-done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="kicker">01 · Daily</div>
          <h3 class="h-3">Simple text cadence</h3>
          <p class="body">
            A daily habit with no schedule. Cadence label is just the word; you
            check in when you do it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 02 · Multi-per-day -->
        <div class="tile-example">
          <div class="tile-example-stage">
            <div class="mock-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <path d="M12 3s6 7 6 12a6 6 0 0 1-12 0c0-5 6-12 6-12z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad-dots">
                  <span class="today-pre">TODAY</span>
                  <span class="sd done"></span>
                  <span class="sd done"></span>
                  <span class="sd pending"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">drink water</div>
              <div class="t-last">3h ago</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell today"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="kicker">02 · Multi-per-day</div>
          <h3 class="h-3">Today's slots, as dots</h3>
          <p class="body">
            3× a day, two done. The dot row top-right is today's progress; the
            week strip is the long view.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 03 · Scheduled -->
        <div class="tile-example">
          <div class="tile-example-stage">
            <div class="mock-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle>
                    <path d="M12 7v5l3 2"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad" style="color: var(--nag-orange);">
                  ⏰ 9:00 am
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">vitamins</div>
              <div class="t-last">due in 12 min</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell today"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="kicker">03 · Scheduled</div>
          <h3 class="h-3">Time-attached, will notify</h3>
          <p class="body">
            A clock + time means a notification fires at that moment. The orange
            cadence label is the tell.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 04 · M·W·F -->
        <div class="tile-example">
          <div class="tile-example-stage">
            <div class="mock-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.7"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  >
                    <path d="M6 6v12M18 6v12M3 9v6M21 9v6M6 12h12"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="t-cad">m·w·f</div>
              </div>
              <div class="t-name">gym</div>
              <div class="t-last">monday</div>
              <div class="t-spacer"></div>
              <div class="mock-week">
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">M</span>
                  <div class="cell done"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">T</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">W</span>
                  <div class="cell missed"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl is-today">T</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">F</span>
                  <div class="cell future"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <span class="lbl">S</span>
                  <div class="cell skip"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="kicker">04 · The week, in detail</div>
          <h3 class="h-3">Every day-state, visible</h3>
          <p class="body">
            Filled = done. Slash = missed. Tiny dot = off-day. Orange ring =
            today. No streaks; just the record.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 05 · Monthly -->
        <div class="tile-example">
          <div class="tile-example-stage">
            <div class="mock-tile">
              <div class="t-top">
                <div class="t-icon">
                  <svg
                    width="14"
                    height="14"
